subject: Football
Draft and Recruitment (Sports)
lead_paragraph: Three playoff spots, and a slew of seedings, will be determined on the final day of the regular season. But for a longer-term effect on the N.F.L., look to the otherwise meaningless game between Jacksonville and Indianapolis.
